  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696850/extras/9f3575b42f1783058f2626e183484784.poster.avif?t=1754297599\" width=540 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696850/extras/9f3575b42f1783058f2626e183484784.webm?t=1754297599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696850/extras/9f3575b42f1783058f2626e183484784.mp4?t=1754297599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>High-Speed Aerial Racing</strong>: Soar through the alien skies at incredible speeds, weaving through energy rings suspended in the atmosphere. Master the art of <strong>precision flying</strong> as you navigate hairpin turns, tight corridors, and gravity-defying drops.<br><br><strong>Time Trial Challenge</strong>: Race against the world in over 20 adrenaline fuelled time trial circuits. Every millisecond counts and only the most skilled pilots will conquer the leaderboard. Can you become the undisputed champion?<br><br><strong>Boost Through Ring Mastery</strong>: Collect speed-boosting rings strategically placed throughout each circuit. Skilfully catching them sequentially not only adds to your speed but also avoids overheating of your flying unit.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696850/extras/a1ff6c7ce058136ee57a1b3f16c4f64c.poster.avif?t=1754297599\" width=540 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696850/extras/a1ff6c7ce058136ee57a1b3f16c4f64c.webm?t=1754297599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696850/extras/a1ff6c7ce058136ee57a1b3f16c4f64c.mp4?t=1754297599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Changing weather conditions</strong>: Adapt your flying skills to the changing weather system and the diverse lighting conditions. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696850/extras/1ea93ce0f936068b20aa9fdbde2080ad.poster.avif?t=1754297599\" width=540 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696850/extras/1ea93ce0f936068b20aa9fdbde2080ad.webm?t=1754297599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696850/extras/1ea93ce0f936068b20aa9fdbde2080ad.mp4?t=1754297599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Alien World Exploration</strong>: Immerse yourself in a visually stunning alien planet and its otherworldly landscapes and mysterious landmarks, Fly at your own leisure, free from the clock pressure. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696850/extras/f808b9b26a25a75bbefee1502871f7f7.poster.avif?t=1754297599\" width=540 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696850/extras/f808b9b26a25a75bbefee1502871f7f7.webm?t=1754297599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696850/extras/f808b9b26a25a75bbefee1502871f7f7.mp4?t=1754297599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Unlockables</strong>: Complete races/achievements to unlock more circuits and skin colours to fly with. Discover the planet's \"secrets\" to unlock the ultimate flying machine…<br><br><strong>Reward system</strong> based on performance (1/2/3 stars)<br><br><strong>Achievements</strong>: Over 60 Steam achievements<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696850/extras/8c023a8e83c75c503ee8f1d4c4b781ce.poster.avif?t=1754297599\" width=538 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696850/extras/8c023a8e83c75c503ee8f1d4c4b781ce.webm?t=1754297599\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696850/extras/8c023a8e83c75c503ee8f1d4c4b781ce.mp4?t=1754297599\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
